   So `(Quotient.mk (I i)) x = (Quotient.mk (I i)) (Quotient.mk (⨅ i, I i) r) = (r + I i) = 0` implies `r ∈ I i`. 

   Hence, `Quotient.mk (⨅ i, I i) r = 0`, because `r ∈ ⨅ i, I i`.

