2. Then for every `i`, `(Quotient.mk (I i)) x = (Quotient.mk (I i)) (Quotient.mk (⨅ i, I i) r) = (Quotient.mk (I i)) r = 0`, hence `r ∈ I i`. 
3. Since this is true for every `i`, `r ∈ ⨅ i, I i`, and thus `x = 0`. 

